SELECT 
    (SME_avg - LAM_avg) AS SME_LAM_diff,
    (LAM_avg - KAM_avg) AS LAM_KAM_diff,
    (KAM_avg - SME_avg) AS KAM_SME_diff
FROM (
    SELECT 
        (SME_sum / SME_count) AS SME_avg,
        (LAM_sum / LAM_count) AS LAM_avg,
        (KAM_sum / KAM_count) AS KAM_avg
    FROM (
        SELECT 
            SUM(CASE WHEN T1.Segment = 'SME' THEN T2.Consumption ELSE 0 END) AS SME_sum,
            SUM(CASE WHEN T1.Segment = 'LAM' THEN T2.Consumption ELSE 0 END) AS LAM_sum,
            SUM(CASE WHEN T1.Segment = 'KAM' THEN T2.Consumption ELSE 0 END) AS KAM_sum,
            COUNT(CASE WHEN T1.Segment = 'SME' THEN T1.CustomerID ELSE NULL END) AS SME_count,
            COUNT(CASE WHEN T1.Segment = 'LAM' THEN T1.CustomerID ELSE NULL END) AS LAM_count,
            COUNT(CASE WHEN T1.Segment = 'KAM' THEN T1.CustomerID ELSE NULL END) AS KAM_count
        FROM customers AS T1
        INNER JOIN yearmonth AS T2
        ON T1.CustomerID = T2.CustomerID
        WHERE T1.Currency = 'CZK' AND SUBSTR(T2.Date, 1, 4) = '2013'
    )
)	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
